Collection and use of personal data
The Application collects localisation information, device model, OS version, language, IP address, IDFA, and UDID. This information is used to improve the quality of service and to provide general statistics about the Garfield: Survival of the Fattest app. Users have the option to create an account with a nickname and email address.
Children’s Privacy
The Application does not actively collect information from users 12 and under. The Application collects localisation information, device model, OS version, language, IP address, and UDID, and geolocation information at country or state level. Younger users are unable to create an account or access sharing features within the Application. We do work with some third party providers in relation to children 12 years of age or under.
These include the following third party providers who do not share our user data with any other third parties.
We work with Flurry analytics restricted version to better understand your use of the app and to improve your experience. For more information on Flurry please see their privacy policy here:
Flurry Restricted
Disclosure
The Application may disclose personal information only if required by law or in case there is the firm belief that such action is necessary to:
Comply with laws and local regulations.
Protect and defend the rights or property of the Application and PIXOWL INC.
In the event that the company is merged or sold.
General Privacy Policy
Collection and use of personal data
The Application collects localisation information, device model, OS version, language, IP address, IDFA, and UDID. This information is used to improve the quality of service and to
provide general statistics about the Garfield: Survival of the Fattest app. Users have the option to create an account with a nickname and email address.
We work with the following third party providers in relation to users 13 and older:
Crashlytics
